I would not allow to provides a custom implementation at this stage, but only to allow to override the method definition inside the interface to add security, open-api and metrics annotation.
Something like this should works
public interface AuthorController extends PanacheCrudController<Author, Long> {
  @Metered
  @RolesAllowed("READER")
  @Operation(summary = "List all authors")
  @Override
  Response list();
}

